# Shipkit Personal Content Gitignore
#
# This file helps you version your personal shipkit content while excluding
# machine-specific or plugin-managed files.
#
# What TO version:
#   - skills/          Your custom skills
#   - steering/        Your behavioral rules (including auto-learned.md)
#   - mcp.json         MCP server configs
#   - config.yaml      Global settings
#   - templates/       Custom project templates
#
# What NOT to version:
#   - .state/          Machine state (sessions, retro pending)
#   - plugins/         Installed from git, not yours
#   - projects/        Machine-specific project paths

# Machine-managed state
.state/

# Plugins (managed via shipkit plugin install)
plugins/

# Project registrations (machine-specific paths)
projects/

# OS and editor files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~
